OL,3,CGrant Hanley & Lyndon Dykes named as
OL,4,Cpart of Scottish World Cup football
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,FScotland's World Cup squad has been
OL,8,Fannounced with Dumfries duo Grant
OL,9,FHanley and Lyndon Dykes named as part
OL,10,Fof the squad.
OL,12,FScotland head coach Steve Clarke
OL,13,Fannounced the 26-man team on Tuesday
OL,14,F19 May.
OL,16,FIt's the first time in nearly 30 years
OL,17,FScotland has qualified for the biggest
OL,18,Ftournament in football - the last time
OL,19,Fthe Tartan Army could follow their
OL,20,Fteam at the World Cup was 1998.
